    <note>Zhang(1) Kangdao [29555] See documentation for mother, Qian Shi under entry for father, Shengqing [248]. Identification as father of Bangji [29557] and, therefore, as son-in-law of Wu(3) Hao [29551], is a guess. Bangji's father may have been Kangdao's younger brother, Kangguang [29556]. However, in Bangji's Mozhuang manlu, he identifies Kangbo [13732] and Kangguo (Kangsun) [248] as his father's elder brothers and does not mention either Kangdao or Kangguang. See also documentation for Bangji.</note>
